166
00:10:31,690 --> 00:10:35,490
I need you to perform another wedding. Can you do that?
我要你帮另一场婚礼证婚，可以吗？

167
00:10:35,700 --> 00:10:38,600
I don't know. Are they Greek Orthodox?
我不知道 他们是希腊正教的信徒吗？

168
00:10:38,830 --> 00:10:40,390
Yeah. Yeah.
对

169
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:45,160
They're my friends, Monica Stephanopolis.
他们是我的朋友 摩妮卡史蒂芬诺波里斯

170
00:10:45,410 --> 00:10:49,670
And Chandler Acidophilus.
跟钱德艾西多菲利斯

171
00:10:53,819 --> 00:10:56,754
Hi.
嗨

172
00:10:58,090 --> 00:10:59,990
Hi.
嗨

173
00:11:02,620 --> 00:11:04,590
Has anyone seen Chandler?
有人看到钱德吗？

174
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:07,820
-I thought he was with you. -He was with me.
-我还以为他跟你在一起 -他刚才是跟我在一起

175
00:11:08,060 --> 00:11:10,760
We're playing a game. Hide-and-seek.
我们在玩游戏 捉迷藏

176
00:11:10,970 --> 00:11:13,870
You can't ask us, son. That's cheating.
你不能问我们，儿子，那是作弊

177
00:11:18,710 --> 00:11:22,370
You're right. Thanks for keeping me honest, Dad.
你说的对，谢谢你纠正我，爸

178
00:11:22,580 --> 00:11:26,380
He can't come here and see the bride in her wedding dress.
他最好别到这里来 他不能看到新娘穿婚纱的样子

179
00:11:26,580 --> 00:11:30,880
When we got married, I saw the groom in the wedding dress.
我还记得我们结婚的时候 我看到新郎穿婚纱的样子

180
00:11:31,850 --> 00:11:35,220
That was after the wedding. It's not bad luck then.
那是婚礼后的事 应该不会带来恶运

181
00:11:35,420 --> 00:11:37,580
Honey, it isn't good luck.
甜心，那也没带来好运

182
00:11:41,930 --> 00:11:45,060
Oh, my God! Monica.
我的天啊！摩妮卡

183
00:11:45,270 --> 00:11:47,000
I know!
我知道！

184
00:11:48,070 --> 00:11:51,470
-How's Chandler doing? -Great.
-钱德还好吗？ -他好极了

185
00:11:51,670 --> 00:11:55,800
He's doing great. Don't you worry about Chandler.
他非常好，别担心钱德

186
00:11:57,080 --> 00:12:00,570
-Phoebe, can I see you for a second? -Yeah.
-菲比，我能跟你谈一下吗？ -没问题

187
00:12:05,990 --> 00:12:08,390
-What's going on? -Chandler's gone again.
-发生了什么事？ -钱德又不见了

188
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:14,030
Why would you play hide-and-seek with someone you know is a flight risk?
为什么你要跟一个可能会逃跑的人 玩捉迷藏呢？

189
00:12:18,170 --> 00:12:21,500
Aaron, you gotta let me go. The guy's hammered.
艾朗，你得放我走 那家伙烂醉如泥

190
00:12:21,670 --> 00:12:26,570
I'm sorry. As long as he's here and conscious, we're still shooting.
对不起，只要他还清醒地待在这里 我们就得继续拍下去

191
00:12:35,820 --> 00:12:39,720
You wouldn't happen to have a very big fork?
你该不会有根大叉子吧？

192
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:44,020
So, I just talked to the director.
我刚刚跟导演谈过

193
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:47,060
That's it. We're done for the day.
就这样，今天就拍到这里为止

194
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:49,620
We finished the scene?
戏拍完了吗？

195
00:12:50,730 --> 00:12:54,530
-You were wonderful. -As were you.
-你表现的很棒 -你也是

196
00:12:55,370 --> 00:12:57,460
So I got your car. It's right outside.
我把你的车开过来了，车子就停在外面

197
00:12:57,710 --> 00:13:00,700
Thank you. You're welcome.
谢谢，别客气

198
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:05,030
No, we gotta go. Come on. Here we go.
不，我们得走了，来吧，要走了

199
00:13:06,550 --> 00:13:08,780
Is that my ass?
那是我的屁股吗？

200
00:13:15,920 --> 00:13:18,590
-There he is! -What?
-他在那里！ -什么？

201
00:13:20,560 --> 00:13:22,620
You won't get away this time!
这次你逃不了，先生！

202
00:13:22,860 --> 00:13:25,990
Unless you want that ass-kicking we talked about!
除非你真的要我痛扁你

203
00:13:27,230 --> 00:13:28,960
Ross!
罗斯！

204
00:13:31,610 --> 00:13:35,270
I'm serious! You're not walking out on my sister!
我是认真的！ 我不准你抛弃我妹妹！

205
00:13:35,480 --> 00:13:37,170
That's right. I'm not.
没错，我不会的

206
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:41,070
-Then where have you been? -I know about Monica.
-那么你跑到哪里去了？ -我知道摩妮卡的事

207
00:13:42,180 --> 00:13:44,240
-You know? -What?
-你知道了？ -什么？

208
00:13:44,450 --> 00:13:47,750
-I heard you and Rachel talking. -About what?
-我听到你跟瑞秋说话 -什么？说什么？

210
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:49,080
You don't know?
你不知道吗？

211
00:13:49,290 --> 00:13:52,660
If somebody doesn't tell me right now....
如果你们不立刻 告诉我发生了什么事…

212
00:13:52,890 --> 00:13:54,660
What, you'll "hi-yah"?
什么？你会“嘿呀”吗？

213
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:58,530
Monica's pregnant.
摩妮卡怀孕了

214
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,200
Oh, my God.
我的天啊

215
00:14:02,470 --> 00:14:06,100
Oh, my God. And you're not freaking out?
我的天啊，你没有被吓跑吗？

216
00:14:06,310 --> 00:14:10,270
I was. Then I went to the gift shop for cigarettes.
我是吓坏了，后来我去了礼品店 因为我的烟都抽完了

217
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:13,780
-Cigarettes? -Big picture, please!
-烟？ -请谈正事

218
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:19,690
So I was in the gift shop, that's when I saw this....
我在礼品店看到这个东西

219
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:25,790
And I thought anything that can fit into this can't be scary.
我想“能穿上这玩意的东西 应该不可怕”

220
00:14:26,360 --> 00:14:29,850
You obviously didn't see Chuckie III.
你明显地你没看过 《灵异入侵-少年军团》

221
00:14:30,530 --> 00:14:33,930
But come on, look at how cute and small this is.
别这样，看看这件小衣服有多可爱

222
00:14:34,170 --> 00:14:38,940
So I got it to give Monica, so she'd know I was okay.
我要把它送给摩妮卡 她会知道我没事的

223
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:40,540
Dude.
兄弟

224
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:44,080
Way to go, son. I knew you'd find him.
做的好，儿子 我知道你一定能找到他

225
00:14:53,450 --> 00:14:55,750
Our little boy is getting married.
我们的小儿子要结婚了

226
00:14:55,990 --> 00:14:58,890
Look at you, so handsome.
看看你，真的好英俊

227
00:14:59,090 --> 00:15:01,390
You look beautiful, Mom.
你看起来很漂亮，妈

228
00:15:04,330 --> 00:15:06,820
You look beautiful too, Dad.
你看起来也很漂亮，爸

229
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:12,230
I love you both.
我爱你们

230
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:14,530
I'm so glad you're here.
我很高兴你来了

231
00:15:20,510 --> 00:15:22,540
Are you Chandler?
你是钱德吗？

232
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:24,750
Are you Joey?
你是乔伊吗？

233
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:32,690
-This is nice. -What?
-这真的是太棒了 -什么？

234
00:15:32,930 --> 00:15:37,490
I've never walked down the aisle knowing it can't end in divorce.
这是我第一次走在红毯上 知道自己不可能会离婚

235
00:15:53,210 --> 00:15:56,650
I wish your grandmother had lived to see this.
真希望你祖母能活着看到这一幕

236
00:15:56,880 --> 00:16:01,250
-She's right there. -Not that old crone. My mother.
-但奶奶就在那边啊 -不是那个老太婆，我是说我妈

237
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:07,090
Congratulations, darling.
恭喜你，亲爱的

238
00:16:07,330 --> 00:16:09,390
We love you, sweetheart.
我们爱你，甜心

239
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:15,430
You look beautiful.
你看起来好美

240
00:16:16,170 --> 00:16:18,760
-ls this new? -Not now.
-这是新买的吗？ -不要在现在讨论

241
00:16:23,110 --> 00:16:25,600
-Who's this? -I'm Father Karabasos.
-他是谁？ -我是卡拉巴索斯神父

242
00:16:25,810 --> 00:16:27,610
He's Greek Orthodox.
他是希腊正教的神父

243
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:30,250
As are you.
你们是希腊正教的信徒

244
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:34,050
Let us begin.
开始举行婚礼吧

245
00:16:35,160 --> 00:16:36,420
Dearly beloved--
亲爱的来宾…

246
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:38,560
That's my line!
那是我的台词

247
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:45,960
I can take it from here. Thanks.
我从这里开始接手，谢谢

248
00:16:48,000 --> 00:16:51,940
Dearly beloved, I'm sorry I'm a little late.
亲爱的来宾 抱歉我来迟了一点

249
00:16:54,480 --> 00:16:57,340
You may be confused by this now...
或许你们会觉得很困惑…

250
00:16:57,610 --> 00:17:01,510
...but you won't be Memorial Day weekend, 2002.
但到了2002年 阵亡将士纪念日，你们就会了解

251
00:17:04,320 --> 00:17:08,020
Let's get started before the groom takes off again.
快点开始举行婚礼 免得新郎又逃跑了

252
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,960
We are gathered here today...
今天我们齐聚在这里…

253
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:19,660
...to join this man...
参加这个男人…

254
00:17:19,870 --> 00:17:24,240
...and this woman in the bonds of holy matrimony.
跟这个女人神圣的婚礼

255
00:17:25,110 --> 00:17:29,300
I've known Monica and Chandler for a long time, and I can't...
我跟摩妮卡及钱德认识很久了 我不能想像…

256
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:34,210
...imagine two people more perfect for each other.
有谁比他们两个更匹配

257
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:41,350
And now, as I've left my notes in my dressing room...
因为我把演讲稿 忘在更衣室里…

258
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:46,150
...we shall proceed to the vows. Monica?
我们直接念誓词吧，摩妮卡？

259
00:17:47,260 --> 00:17:50,530
-He took off? -Go on. Go on.
-他逃走了？ -快点

260
00:17:55,900 --> 00:17:59,900
Chandler, for so long...
钱德，从小…

261
00:18:00,340 --> 00:18:04,070
...I wondered if I would ever find my prince.
我就在想 我能不能找到我的白马王子

262
00:18:04,340 --> 00:18:06,240
My soul mate.
我的灵魂伴侣

263
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:09,310
Then three years ago, at another wedding...
三年前，在另一场婚礼…

264
00:18:09,580 --> 00:18:12,180
...I turned to a friend for comfort.
我向朋友寻求安慰

265
00:18:12,420 --> 00:18:17,620
And instead, I found everything that I'd been looking for my whole life.
结果我找到了 我一直在找的一切

266
00:18:20,430 --> 00:18:22,260
And now...
现在…

267
00:18:23,330 --> 00:18:25,200
...here we are...
我们在这里…

268
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:28,500
...with our future before us.
一起迎接未来

269
00:18:29,770 --> 00:18:32,470
And I only want to spend it with you.
我只想跟你在一起

270
00:18:33,810 --> 00:18:37,900
My prince. My soul mate.
我的白马王子 我的灵魂伴侣

272
00:18:38,110 --> 00:18:40,210
My friend.
我的朋友

273
00:18:42,980 --> 00:18:45,420
Unless you don't want to.
除非你不愿意

274
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:49,350
You go.
轮到你了

275
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:51,820
Chandler?
钱德？

276
00:18:52,990 --> 00:18:55,220
No, that's okay.
不，没关系

277
00:18:59,470 --> 00:19:03,960
I thought this would be the most difficult thing I ever had to do.
我以为这是我必须做的 最困难的一件事

278
00:19:05,510 --> 00:19:10,000
But when I saw you walking down that aisle, I realized it's simple.
但我看到你走过红毯时 我认识到它真的很简单

279
00:19:12,650 --> 00:19:13,940
I love you.
我爱你

280
00:19:15,850 --> 00:19:21,050
Any surprises that come our way, it's okay, because I will always love you.
不论出现什么样的惊喜 没关系，因为我会永远爱你

281
00:19:23,290 --> 00:19:27,520
You are the person I was meant to spend the rest of my life with.
我注定要跟你共渡余生

282
00:19:27,790 --> 00:19:30,020
You want to know if I'm sure?
你想知道我确不确定吗？

283
00:19:33,530 --> 00:19:36,470
You may now kiss the bride.
你可以吻新娘了

284
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:43,910
I guess by the powers vested in me by the State of New York...
我要以纽约州跟网友们…

285
00:19:44,180 --> 00:19:46,650
...and the lnternet guys...
赋给我的权力…

286
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:52,980
...I now pronounce you husband and wife.
我现在宣布你们结为夫妇

287
00:19:53,390 --> 00:19:56,220
Oh, wait. Do you take each other?
等一下，你们愿意吗？

288
00:19:56,420 --> 00:19:58,720
-I do. -I do.
-我愿意 -我愿意

289
00:19:58,930 --> 00:20:00,520
Yeah, you do!
太棒了，你们都愿意！

290
00:20:01,900 --> 00:20:03,090
Rings?
戒指

291
00:20:03,330 --> 00:20:05,060
Oh, crap.
喔，该死，好吧

292
00:20:06,870 --> 00:20:08,600
Let's do the rings.
来戴婚戒吧

293
00:20:19,850 --> 00:20:22,370
We good? Yeah? Good?
可以吗？

294
00:20:23,620 --> 00:20:25,350
Once again...
我要再一次…

295
00:20:25,590 --> 00:20:29,110
...I pronounce you husband and wife.
宣布你们结为夫妇

296
00:20:29,390 --> 00:20:31,550
Now kiss her again.
你可以再吻新娘一次

297
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:48,440
I love you.
我爱你

298
00:20:48,710 --> 00:20:50,840
And I know about the baby.
我知道宝宝的事了

299
00:20:51,710 --> 00:20:53,740
-What baby? -Our baby.
-什么宝宝？ -我们的宝宝

300
00:20:53,950 --> 00:20:55,710
We have a baby?
我们有宝宝了？

301
00:20:57,280 --> 00:20:59,720
Phoebe found your pregnancy test.
菲比发现了你的验孕棒

302
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:02,080
I didn't take a pregnancy test.
我没有验孕

303
00:21:02,290 --> 00:21:04,120
Then who did?
那么是谁验了孕？

304
00:21:04,890 --> 00:21:07,420
Look at them.
看看他们

305
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:10,560
And they're gonna have a baby.
他们要有孩子了

306
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000


307
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
